&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Band 6 Junior Sister / Charge Nurse to join the team on Stannon Ward, Level 11. Stannon Ward is a 25 bedded mixed Health Care of the Elderly Ward and we pride Ourselves in providing a high standard of care for this client group. Stannon Ward is a recognised dementia friendly ward and is the longest standing HCE Ward in the Trust. If you are interested in developing your skills further in a senior role in this clinical area we would like to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like an informal discussion about the post please contact Senior Matthew Potter on extension 32671 or 431388&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;***Preference will be given to internal Trust staff, as well as ‘Priority’ and &#39;At Risk&#39; status including NHS At Risk staff throughout Devon who are able to display recent relevant experience as dictated by the Person Specification.***&lt;/p&gt;
